### ========================================
### CovAuto API - HTTP Request voorbeelden
### ========================================
### Gebruik in VS Code met de REST Client extensie
### of importeer in Postman / Bruno.
###
### Alle wachtwoorden: Demo1234!
### ========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@plannerToken = VERVANG_MET_TOKEN_UIT_LOGIN
@monteurToken = VERVANG_MET_TOKEN_UIT_LOGIN

# ========================================
# 1. AUTHENTICATIE
# ========================================

### Login als planner (Noord)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "planner.noord",
  "password": "Demo1234!"
}

###

### Login als monteur (Jan - Noord team)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "monteur.jan",
  "password": "Demo1234!"
}

###

### Login als monteur (Sven - Zuid team)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "monteur.sven",
  "password": "Demo1234!"
}

# ========================================
# 2. TEAMS
# ========================================

### Alle teams ophalen (alleen Planner)
GET {{baseUrl}}/teams
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Team 1 ophalen (Noord Service)
GET {{baseUrl}}/teams/1
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Team 2 ophalen (Zuid Service)
GET {{baseUrl}}/teams/2
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

# ========================================
# 3. WERKORDERS - Basisoperaties
# ========================================

### Alle werkorders ophalen (standaard: pagina 1, 10 per pagina, gesorteerd op createdAt desc)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Één werkorder ophalen
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Werkorders ophalen als monteur (alleen eigen team zichtbaar)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders
Authorization: Bearer {{monteurToken}}

# ========================================
# 4. WERKORDERS - Filtering
# ========================================

### Filter op status: Nieuw
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders?status=Nieuw
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Filter op prioriteit: Kritiek
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders?priority=Kritiek
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Filter op titel (bevat "ketel")
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders?title=ketel
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Filter op klantnaam
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders?customerName=Fam
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Filter op geschatte uren (tussen 3 en 6 uur)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders?minEstimatedHours=3&maxEstimatedHours=6
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Combineer meerdere filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders?status=Gepland&priority=Normaal&minEstimatedHours=4
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

# ========================================
# 5. WERKORDERS - Sorting
# ========================================

### Sorteer op titel (A-Z)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders?sortBy=title&sortDirection=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Sorteer op geschatte uren (hoogste eerst)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders?sortBy=estimatedHours&sortDirection=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Sorteer op geplande datum (vroegste eerst)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders?sortBy=scheduledFor&sortDirection=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

# ========================================
# 6. WERKORDERS - Pagination
# ========================================

### Pagina 1, 5 items per pagina
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders?page=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Pagina 2, 5 items per pagina
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders?page=2&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

###

### Combineer alles: filter + sorteer + pagineer
GET {{baseUrl}}/workorders?status=Nieuw&sortBy=estimatedHours&sortDirection=asc&page=1&pageSize=3
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}

# ========================================
# 7. WERKORDERS - Aanmaken
# ========================================

### Nieuwe werkorder aanmaken (alleen Planner)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workorders
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Installatie zonneboiler",
  "description": "Nieuwe zonneboiler installeren op het dak.",
  "estimatedHours": 5.5,
  "status": 0,
  "priority": 2,
  "scheduledFor": "2024-03-01T09:00:00Z",
  "customerName": "Fam. Pietersen",
  "address": "Zonnelaan 42, Utrecht",
  "serviceTeamId": 1
}

# ========================================
# 8. RAPPORTEN (alleen Planner)
# ========================================

### Rapport voor team Noord (teamId = 1) over januari 2024
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/workorders/team/1
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "to": "2024-01-31T23:59:59Z"
}

###

### Rapport voor team Zuid (teamId = 2) over januari 2024
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/workorders/team/2
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "to": "2024-01-31T23:59:59Z"
}

###

### Bulk rapporten PARALLEL voor beide teams
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/workorders/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "teamIds": [1, 2],
  "from": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "to": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z"
}

###

### Performance vergelijking: sequentieel vs. parallel
### Laat zien hoe Task.WhenAll sneller is dan één voor één await
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/performance-comparison
Authorization: Bearer {{plannerToken}}